room_title: Escape room "The Rooftop" by Enter Locked Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
room_description: Mr. Waffles has done it again! That crazy cat has gotten out of the window and is roaming the neighborhood. You finally find him hiding on top of an abandoned building that's scheduled to get demolished in one hour. Can you save your missing cat and get off of the rooftop before it blows up?
